==English==
===Noun===
'''checkers''' 
# ''(US, singular):'' A [[game]] for two [[player]]s played on a [[chessboard]]; the players have 12 pieces each, and the [[object]] is to [[capture]] all the [[opponent]]’s pieces by [[jump]]ing over them. Other European varieties have larger boards and more playing pieces.
# ''(US, plural):'' the playing pieces in the game of checkers.

